comment: Spatial gaussian defined on the cuticle nodes. Used for distributing or smoothing point contact forces.
The Gaussian's value is calculated based on the direct distance between the two nodes (curvature of the cuticle is not considered)
The Gaussian's definition is given; the distance between the nodes is limited to given max threshold, however, the Gaussian's values are normalised to 1
Format: <cuticle Node>: [list of <cuticle Node>: Gaussian's value, ...]
